==English==
===Noun===
'''pouch''' (''plural:'' pouches)

# A small [[bag]] usually closed with a [[drawstring]]
# A [[pocket]] in which a [[marsupial]] [[carry|carries]] its [[young]]
# Any [[pocket]] or [[bag]] shaped object; as, a posing pouch

